name: DEF Up
effectName: Increase DEF of Servant on space by 30%

name: Damage Cut
effectName: Apply a state that reduces damage taken by 500 to Servant on space

name: HP Recovery Amount Up
effectName: Increase HP Recovery amount by 50% to Servant on space

name: HP Recover Each Turn
effectName: Apply a state that restores HP by 2000 to Servant on space

name: NP Gain Each Turn
effectName: Apply a state that increases NP Gauge by 30% each turn to Servant on space (Increase Charge by 1 if enemy)

name: Critical Strength Up
effectName: Increase Critical Strength of Servant on space by 30%

name: Gain C. Stars Each Turn
effectName: Apply a state where Servant on space gains C. Stars [10 Stars] each turn (Increase Critical Rate by 20% if enemy (Permanent))

name: Decrease HP [Demerit]
effectName: Apply a state that decreases HP by 3000 to Servant on space (1 turn)

name: ATK Up
effectName: Increase ATK of Servant on space by 20%

name: Skill Seal [Demerit]
effectName: Inflict Skill Seal on this space's Servant <Cannot be nullified by skills etc>
